# Language — Agent Communication

## Think and respond in Simplified Chinese (简体中文)

Use Simplified Chinese for all **agent-to-user** communication — replies, explanations, summaries, questions back to the user.

Exception: if the user writes in English, reply in English.

## All code, comments, and docs stay in English

See `documentation-language.mdc` for the full rule (English-only in code, rules, README, JSDoc, Python).
